<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4868] Log4J watcher - setting the root logger adds a logger for the empty string</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4868</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Root cause for &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4867&quot; title=&quot;Admin UI - setting loglevel on root throws RangeError&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-4867&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-4867&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  Trying to set the root logging category results in the addition of a category that&apos;s the empty string.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12649784">SOLR-4868</key>
            <summary>Log4J watcher - setting the root logger adds a logger for the empty string</summary>
